text: Qiu Yike (born 18 January 1985), is a male Chinese international table tennis player. He won the bronze medal at the 2005 World Table Tennis Championships Mixed Doubles and 2007 World Table Tennis Championships – Mixed Doubles with Cao Zhen. ==See also== * List of table tennis players ==References== Category:Living people Category:Sportspeople from Chengdu Category:Table tennis players from Sichuan Category:1985 births Category:Chinese male table tennis players Category:World Table Tennis Championships medalists
